# Market Catalyst Alert System - Product Plan

Last reviewed: 2026-06-15

This file is the authoritative implementation guide for turning the existing
local NQ Catalyst project into a secure subscription web application.

## Checklist Rules

- Use `[x]` only when the feature is implemented and verified.
- Keep `[ ]` when the feature is missing, mocked, local-only, or incomplete.
- Do not mark a parent milestone complete until every required child item is
  complete.
- When checking an item, add an evidence line with the date, files changed, and
